HEADWORD: Infantile
<hw>In"fan*tile</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>infantilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>infantile</ets>. See
<er>Infant</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to infancy, or to an
infant; similar to, or characteristic of, an infant; childish; <as>as,
<ex>infantile</ex> behavior</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

